claim.claim-text:
36. A multi-layer optical recording medium, comprising: 
user data areas on each recording layer; 
grooves formed on the user data areas; 
user data wobbles formed on at least one lateral surface of each groove of one of the recording layers; and 
lead out wobbles, which differ from the user data wobbles of the one recording layer, formed in an area beyond a predetermined radius of the one recording layer.
